<h3>The Facepunch (re)design Challenge</h3>

<p>There was a Facepunch redesign contest in the <a href="http://www.facepunch.com/forumdisplay.php?f=353">Web Development</a> section of Facepunch and I decided to join and try it out.</p>

<p>I've made two, but I decided to only release one. The one that I released is minimal because of the mobile version that I wanted to support too. The demo link: <br>
